A warm, sunlit outdoor basketball court at an elementary school, illustrated in the gentle, whimsical style of Studio Ghibli. Dozens of young children in colorful uniforms swarm around basketball hoops, orange balls arcing through the air in every direction. A tall adult figure stands at the center, arms outstretched, catching and returning balls with joyful energy. The scene is dynamic and chaotic yet heartwarming, with soft watercolor-like textures, dappled sunlight filtering through nearby tropical trees, and a sense of happy exhaustion. Children's faces beam with determination and laughter. In the background, simple school buildings with red roofs and Singapore's lush greenery frame the scene. The color palette is warm golds, fresh greens, and cheerful primary colors, evoking community spirit and the beautiful chaos of a school sports day.
